ultimate goal is simple: eliminate your enemies and claim victory.\n\n**Key Features:**\n\n- **Immersive VR Experience:** Feel the intensity of battle as you command your forces from the front lines.\n- **Strategic Gameplay:** Plan your attacks, manage resources, and build a powerful army.\n- **Diverse Maps:** Explore different environments, each with its own unique challenges and opportunities.\n\nAre you ready to take on the challenge and become the ultimate VR RTS commander?", "short_description": "Immerse yourself in the heart of battle as you command your forces in a fully immersive virtual reality experience. Gather resources, build powerful armies, and outmaneuver your opponents in epic clashes. With intuitive VR controls, you'll feel like a true military commander, strategizing and executing your plans with precision. Are you ready to take on the challenge and become the ultimate VR RTS dominator?"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://artisoft.pl/policies/vk_v1.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Artisoft", "support_website_url": "https://vk.artisoft.pl/support.html", "website_url": "https://vk.artisoft.pl/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "275629210202852"}, {"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "644354873106712"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "27752221771058288"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": 