--H3D4GNbVcMHZmyeSem95oOKkC9bGFNCZ0flDgg&oe=67753F69"}, "display_name": "Virtual Kingdoms", "keywords": ["strategy", "battle", "command", "fight", "knight"], "long_description": "**Immerse yourself in the heat of battle.**\n\nExperience the thrill of real-time strategy in a fully immersive virtual reality environment. Choose from a variety of maps, each with its own unique terrain and challenges. Select your opponents and prepare for an epic clash.\n\n**Command Your Army from the Front Lines.**\n\nGather resources, build crucial structures, and train powerful units to dominate the battlefield. With intuitive VR controls, you'll feel like a true military commander, directing your forces with precision and strategy.\n\n**Annihilate Your Enemies.**\n\nOutmaneuver your opponents, launch devastating attacks, and seize strategic points to gain the upper hand. The ultimate goal is simple: eliminate your enemies and claim victory.\n\n**Key Features:**\n\n- **Immersive VR Experience:** Feel the intensity of battle as you command your forces from the front lines.\n- **Strategic Gameplay:** Plan your attacks, manage resources, and build a powerful army.\n- **Diverse Maps:** Explore different environments, each with its own unique challenges and opportunities.\n\nAre you ready to take on the challenge and become the ultimate VR RTS commander?", "short_description": "Immerse yourself in the heart of battle as you command your forces in a fully immersive virtual reality experience. Gather resources, build powerful armies, and outmaneuver your opponents in epic clashes. With intuitive VR controls, you'll feel like a true military commander, strategizing and executing your plans with precision. Are you ready to take on the challenge and become the ultimate VR RTS dominator?"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://artisoft.pl/policies/vk_v1.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Artisoft", "support_website_url": "https://vk.ar